project_descr: Promotion of UN’s work and impact of its interventions in Albania by speaking with One Voice and advocating for issues of concern to the country, spread awareness about UN’s key partners and UN’s contribution to the Albanian national priorities.

outputs.output_descr: The project works to spread awareness around the new Programme of Cooperation, advocate for issues that the UN stands for in Albania, increase the visibility and profile of the United Nations by focusing on substance and results and promote partnerships.
